Reasoning: 
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is the most likely category as the paper deals with regular languages and their hierarchies. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is also likely as the paper discusses the complexity of membership problems for various classes of Boolean hierarchies. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possibility as the paper develops new algorithms for deciding membership in these hierarchies. 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is another possibility as the paper uses forbidden-chain characterizations to obtain its results. 
- cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) is also a possibility as the paper deals with mathematical structures such as hierarchies and predicates.
